"{\"uid\": \"semafor.com-article-08-07-2024-africa-astronomy-olympics-meeting-for-first-time\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Intelligence for the New World Economy  The International Astronomical Union\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s General Assembly \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 held every four years and so, inevitably, known as the Olympics of astronomy \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 is being hosted in Africa for the first time.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 228, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 32nd meeting of the world\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s top space researchers started in Cape Town Monday.\", \"from\": 230, \"to\": 314, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"South Africa and several other southern African nations, alongside Australia, will be home to the world\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s largest radio telescope, the Square Kilometer Array, the first stage of which is set for completion in 2027.\", \"from\": 316, \"to\": 532, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 316, \"end\": 328, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999953416470861, \"rank\": 1.8940079130572654e-06, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}, {\"begin\": 383, \"end\": 392, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.6419824478907302, \"rank\": 0.541960315488991, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That, as well as the continent\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s growing scientific prowess, led to the decision to host the assembly there.\", \"from\": 533, \"to\": 643, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThis is a significant milestone,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d one African astronomer wrote in The Conversation: Space science in Africa \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009chas grown and strengthened tremendously over the past decade.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  Intelligence for the New World Economy  Sign up for SemaforAfrica\", \"from\": 645, \"to\": 892, \"entities\": []}]}"